                    <div class="post-heading">
                        <h1>Radiometric Enhancement</h1>
                        <h2 class="subheading">Correcting for Radiometric Distortion</h2>
                        <span class="meta">Posted by <a href="#">Dennis Sherman</a> on January 29, 2017</span>
